Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.10,0:00:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次觀賞的人 請注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.83,0:00:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要保持房間明亮\N坐遠一點再看喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.61,0:00:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於找到了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.55,0:00:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次絕對不會錯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.12,0:00:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要再幾十分就到了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.12,0:00:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就快了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.69,0:00:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上妳就能見到他了，莉采兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.37,0:00:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要能在一起\N就覺得好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.38,0:00:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使被罵了\N也還是好喜歡好喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.38,0:00:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算一副臭臉\N也是那麼迷人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.48,0:00:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請實現我的願望吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.39,0:00:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來吧 一起來吧\N一起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.49,0:01:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來吧 一起來吧\N一起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.49,0:01:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來吧......
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.59,0:01:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一．起．來．吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.46,0:01:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自那天以來的悸動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.94,0:01:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論何時都還感覺的到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.31,0:01:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管到哪裡都只想和你一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.45,0:01:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管做什麼都好讓人心動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.95,0:01:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陷入戀愛的人們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.86,0:01:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都好像魔法師一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.06,0:01:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使是微不足道的小事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.83,0:01:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可以讓人高興起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.40,0:01:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要能在一起就覺得好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.34,0:01:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使被罵了也還是好喜歡好喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.41,0:01:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算一副臭臉也是那麼迷人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.58,0:01:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請實現我的願望吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.18,0:01:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來吧 一起來吧\N一起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.25,0:02:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來吧 一起來吧\N一起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.42,0:02:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來吧......
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.49,0:02:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次一起來吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.86,0:02:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然!不請自來的小嬌妻!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.24,0:02:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混帳~~~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.91,0:02:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混帳~~~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.71,0:02:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混帳~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.55,0:02:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少擋老子的路~~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.33,0:02:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨~大家早啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.83,0:02:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也要打起精神上課喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.74,0:02:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?老師，那個戒指是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.41,0:03:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，被發現了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.34,0:03:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,婚禮是什麼時候啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.54,0:03:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菜搞老師，難道妳要結婚了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.41,0:03:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公是怎樣的人啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.35,0:03:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦，真是~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.62,0:03:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦岩城同學\N老師要結婚了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.02,0:03:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那，那又怎樣\N跟我又沒有關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.23,0:03:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼婚禮嘛!什麼結婚嘛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.84,0:03:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混帳~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.29,0:03:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去，真是超不爽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.89,0:03:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之啊我沒學到教訓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.26,0:03:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又為了比我年長的女人失戀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.23,0:04:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去!我怎麼老是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.60,0:04:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.07,0:04:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦!老公~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.14,0:04:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於見到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.11,0:04:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一天我已經等了好久好久了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.78,0:04:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公?老公你在哪兒啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.09,0:04:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快，快掛了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.29,0:04:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦，怎麼在那種地方...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.93,0:04:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳妳妳、妳誰啊妳!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.53,0:04:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊!這樣不行這樣不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.24,0:04:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉沒有事先說明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.74,0:04:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從今天起正式成為您的妻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.17,0:04:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫莉采兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.54,0:04:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是妻子耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.68,0:04:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳...不會是腦袋秀逗了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.18,0:04:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連入籍都辦好了，你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.32,0:04:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這、這啥啊!?我才15歲耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.06,0:04:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這叫國家權力!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.06,0:05:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.06,0:05:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什什、什麼啊?你們這群歐吉桑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.90,0:05:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待在那種地方做什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.27,0:05:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是歐吉桑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.14,0:05:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.34,0:05:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉采兒的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.40,0:05:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾爹!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.91,0:05:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾、乾爹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.64,0:05:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是乾爹!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.64,0:05:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算你們那麼說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.08,0:05:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老爸!老媽!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.98,0:05:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是年輕貌美的乾媽們就好了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.22,0:05:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問題不在那兒吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.35,0:05:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼興奮嘛，老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.15,0:05:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天可是我們的結婚紀念日啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.37,0:05:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.67,0:05:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.94,0:05:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉采兒可是以某DNA為基礎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.50,0:05:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結合了國家最先進的技術所\N造出之細胞集合體的原型人種啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.24,0:05:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少跟我說那些莫名其妙的東西!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.62,0:05:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈，第一次惹老公生氣\N又第一次被扔又第一次被摔耶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.45,0:06:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不放開~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.46,0:06:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次被甩來甩去耶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.65,0:06:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就由我向各位說明吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.35,0:06:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為是國家機密所以一切無可奉告!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.49,0:06:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.42,0:06:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那算啥啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.49,0:06:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何，莉采兒成為你的妻子\N那已經是國家的決定事項了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可不能讓她哭泣喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.23,0:06:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不可以喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.93,0:06:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要擅自作主!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.50,0:06:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，憑我丈夫那\N微薄的薪水光養這
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.30,0:06:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正值發育期的孩子\N就已經夠辛苦的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.44,0:06:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對，對啊\N我連自己的書房都沒有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.08,0:06:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且這間房子還有\N30多年的利息要繳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.18,0:07:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這之上要是\N家裡人再增加的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.95,0:07:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的零用錢可是零\N零耶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.19,0:07:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你直昇部長...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.32,0:07:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終生免繳水電費和\N醫療建保費...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.26,0:07:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房屋貸款從此\N一筆勾消...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.77,0:07:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚餐吃炒三鮮\N可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.90,0:07:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，太太，不用那麼客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.27,0:07:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,球賽要開始了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.54,0:07:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼才一下\N大家就一團和氣啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.21,0:07:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管老爸老媽是怎麼想的\N反正我是不會承認的啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.21,0:07:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.41,0:07:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.48,0:07:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新婚初夜新郎應該要把新娘子\N抱到床上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.85,0:07:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新娘子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.12,0:07:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱抱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.06,0:07:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呀，老公你真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.86,0:07:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦，性子那麼急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.07,0:07:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只對年長的女人\N有興趣!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.07,0:08:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 這輩子都不會\N把妳放在眼裡的啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.08,0:08:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.94,0:08:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要比你年長就可以了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.58,0:08:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，只要妳能的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.25,0:08:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，我會加油的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.32,0:08:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白~痴!那種事是不可能的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.82,0:08:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比我年幼就是一輩子比我年幼\N比我年長就是一輩子比我年長啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.83,0:08:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且不管怎麼看妳都只是小學生嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.83,0:08:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒什麼好說的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.53,0:08:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都不行嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.47,0:08:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.10,0:08:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣都...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.17,0:08:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少煩我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.24,0:08:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可能會哭喔!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.34,0:08:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種把戲對我沒用啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.71,0:08:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓她哭啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.11,0:08:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉采兒，不可以哭喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.71,0:08:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是好孩子要忍耐喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.45,0:08:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍一忍，忍一忍嘛\N莉采兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.35,0:08:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別哭\N別哭喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.72,0:08:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉采兒...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.32,0:08:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點到避難所去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.63,0:08:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼避難所啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.49,0:08:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.96,0:08:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.01,0:09:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼\N沒什麼好說的呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.38,0:09:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公你這個大笨蛋~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.25,0:09:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不快收回你剛剛說的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.78,0:09:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個家會完蛋的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.18,0:09:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這這、這是什麼啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.38,0:09:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉采兒眼淚的成分\N幾乎跟硝化甘油一樣啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.62,0:09:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變成這樣我們也阻止不了了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.16,0:09:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別哭啦，莉采兒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.40,0:09:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就先讓妳住下來啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.90,0:09:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.51,0:09:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.51,0:09:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千真萬確嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.28,0:09:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還能怎麼辦啊!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.78,0:09:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公我最喜歡你了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.18,0:09:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒說妳可以抱我~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.79,0:09:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次被老公丟向夕陽耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.79,0:09:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度很快就能修復了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.56,0:10:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算全部被炸毀也只要兩三天就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.73,0:10:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候，機密費用還真是好用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.07,0:10:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁炒三鮮冷掉之前\N快來吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.70,0:10:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來來，啤酒再多喝點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.31,0:10:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.32,0:10:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯~好讓人期待喔\N新婚初夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.92,0:10:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦!\N是初夜耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.09,0:10:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公再等一下唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.83,0:10:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好倒楣的一天啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.10,0:11:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.46,0:11:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛!\N至少先敲個門吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.37,0:11:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小女子不才，還請您多多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.37,0:11:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛打扮成這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.47,0:11:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦!新婚初夜\N當然要穿長襦絆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.81,0:11:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.48,0:11:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先進來囉~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.81,0:11:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂喂喂!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.32,0:11:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭，老公你怎麼那麼猴急嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.12,0:11:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在打什麼鬼主意啊!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.62,0:11:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圖書館的書上有寫說新婚夫妻要在\N同一個被窩裡做「好事」啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.49,0:11:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那什麼書啊!要睡到別的房間去睡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.76,0:11:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.13,0:11:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不不，不要哭啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.50,0:11:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我能在這房間睡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.67,0:11:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去!真拿妳沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.40,0:11:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我睡囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.51,0:11:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那裡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.54,0:11:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的位置在這兒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.18,0:12:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.55,0:12:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你對我這麼溫柔\N我好高興喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.02,0:12:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼傻話\N哪裡算溫柔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.82,0:12:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然講的那麼不情願的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.19,0:12:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是還是讓我睡同一間房間了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.83,0:12:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為讓妳哭的話就麻煩大啦\N白痴~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.81,0:12:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，等一等\N不行、別哭、別哭啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.86,0:12:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊! 衝啊! 衝啊!\N老公啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.37,0:12:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊! 衝啊! 衝啊!\N老公啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.57,0:13:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊! 衝啊! 衝啊!\N老公啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.11,0:13:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡你了 衝啊衝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.38,0:13:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男人和女人真是難以理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.75,0:13:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了查清楚我去了圖書館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.42,0:13:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然對比他年幼的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.59,0:13:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公是一點興趣也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.73,0:13:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是人家好喜歡你\N所以我不會哭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.51,0:13:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不氣餒，不逃避\N更不會失去勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.75,0:13:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信總有一天春天會到來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.65,0:13:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿出認真的力量\N認真的力量往前衝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.29,0:13:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊! 衝啊! 衝啊!\N老公啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.80,0:14:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊! 衝啊! 衝啊!\N老公啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.17,0:14:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊! 衝啊! 衝啊!\N老公啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.47,0:14:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好喜歡你 衝啊衝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.31,0:14:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是莉采兒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.18,0:14:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡的東西是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.55,0:14:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...是老公!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.05,0:14:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說最重要的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.58,0:14:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...是老公!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.15,0:14:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要努力，讓老公對我割目相看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.45,0:14:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(次回 獨佔!大人的時間!?)\N會哼哼哼~的去唷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.43,0:14:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是莉采兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.33,0:14:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡的東西是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.70,0:14:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...是老公!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.07,0:14:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說最重要的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.60,0:14:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...是老公!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.20,0:14:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最最最~喜歡老公了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.80,0:14:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是他老是在生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.17,0:14:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是太累了呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.68,0:14:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要笑瞇瞇的話\N每天都會很快樂說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.18,0:14:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好~讓老公笑瞇瞇大作戰!\N要加油嘍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.18,0:14:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要努力，讓老公對我割目相看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.35,0:14:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(次回 獨佔!大人的時間!?)\N會哼哼哼~的去唷!
